OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777903630
OL,3,CPlans to ship Guernsey's contaminated
OL,4,Csoil to the UK
OL,6,FSoil containing high concentrations of
OL,7,Fthe chemical PFOS at Guernsey Airport
OL,8,Fcould be shipped to the UK at a cost
OL,9,Fof #16.5 million.
OL,11,FThe soil was excavated from various
OL,12,Fplaces around the airport in 2012, and
OL,13,Fthe site of a freight plane crash in a
OL,14,Ffield alongside Forest Road.
OL,16,FPFOS commonly known as a forever
OL,17,Fchemical, which means it can't be
OL,18,Fbroken down in the environment and may
OL,19,Fpose a risk to health, was used in
OL,20,Ffirefighting foam between 1970 to 2000.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777903630
OL,3,CPlans to ship Guernsey's contaminated
OL,4,Csoil to the UK
OL,6,FAt the time, treatment solutions to
OL,7,Fremove PFOS from the soil were not
OL,8,Freadily available, so the soil was
OL,9,Fstored in a mound at the entrance to
OL,10,Fthe airport with a membrane to prevent
OL,11,Fthe chemical escaping. But now the
OL,12,Fgovernment is concerned about the
OL,13,Fsignificant pollution risk, unless
OL,14,Fsteps are taken to treat of further
OL,15,Fcontain the soil.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777903630
OL,3,CPlans to ship Guernsey's contaminated
OL,4,Csoil to the UK
OL,6,FDeputy Mark Helyar, President of the
OL,7,FStates Trading and Supervisory Board
OL,8,Fsays they have to act now: "We've been
OL,9,Fgiven notice effectively by the
OL,10,Fenvironmental regulator that we need
OL,11,Fto do something about the toxic
OL,12,Fchemicals that are in this site."
OL,14,FHe added: "There is evidence they are
OL,15,Fstarting to escape into the
OL,16,Fenvironment, once they are in the
OL,17,Fenvironment they become extremely
OL,18,Fexpensive to clean up so we need to do
OL,19,Fsomething about it as soon as
OL,20,Fpossible."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777903630
OL,3,CPlans to ship Guernsey's contaminated
OL,4,Csoil to the UK
OL,6,FOnce in the UK the soil will undergo a
OL,7,Fprocess called 'soil washing' which
OL,8,Finvolves using an abrasive and water
OL,9,Fto rinse the contamination out. The
OL,10,Fchemicals are then extracted from the
OL,11,Fwater by passing it through a carbon
OL,12,Ffilter and the destroyed by heat
OL,13,Ftreatment.
OL,15,FSand and gravel from the soil can then
OL,16,Fbe re-used , and any residual
OL,17,Fcontaminated material will be disposed
OL,18,Fof at specialist site for hazardous
OL,19,Fmaterial.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777903630
OL,3,CPlans to ship Guernsey's contaminated
OL,4,Csoil to the UK
OL,6,FOther processes to rid the soil of the
OL,7,FPFOS on island had been considered,
OL,8,Fbut were determined to be too costly,
OL,9,Ftechnically not viable, unproven at
OL,10,Flarge scale, or not providing a
OL,11,Fsuitably long-term solution to the
OL,12,Fpollution risk.
OL,14,FThe States will be asked to approve
OL,15,Fthe project in June. If given the go
OL,16,Fahead a planning application will be
OL,17,Fneeded, and environmental impact
OL,18,Fassessment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777903630
OL,3,CPlans to ship Guernsey's contaminated
OL,4,Csoil to the UK
OL,6,FThe work is expected to take around 10
OL,7,Fmonths to complete, and to minimise
OL,8,Fthe risk of any chemicals being
OL,9,Freleased during the operation it will
OL,10,Fbe timed to avoid the winter months-
OL,11,F so it's not expected to start until
OL,12,Fearly 2027.
OL,14,FThis isn't the only measure that's
OL,15,Fbeen taken to protect water supplies
OL,16,Ffollowing the detection of PFOS.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777903630
OL,3,CPlans to ship Guernsey's contaminated
OL,4,Csoil to the UK
OL,6,FThese include a dedicated treatment
OL,7,Fplant that filters groundwater at the
OL,8,Fairport, and a bypass to allow water
OL,9,Ffrom streams to be diverted away from
OL,10,FSt Saviour's reservoir, and discharged
OL,11,Fto sea.
OL,13,FProperties near the airport with
OL,14,Fprivate boreholes were also offered
OL,15,Fconnection to the mains network.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
