FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777903630
OL,3,CPlans to ship Guernsey's contaminated
OL,4,Csoil to the UK
OL,6,FIn Jersey the chemical PFAS which is
OL,7,Fpart of the same family of chemicals
OL,8,Fleaked into private borehole water
OL,9,Fsupplies after they were used in
OL,10,Ffirefighting foams at Jersey Airport
OL,11,Fin 1991.
OL,13,FJersey's Government offered blood
OL,14,Ftests to those effected.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
